Johara Anti-Hair Fall Serum is a power packed non-sticky, light weight, silicone free serum for reducing hair fall, improve hair regrowth, ultimate nutrition, and hydration of hair. Suitable for all hair types and texture.

Description:

It is carefully formulated by using patented actives like Cococin™*, Saberry®*, PeptiSelect®*, Cosmoperine®*, Peanut Shell Extract along with Nigellin® Amber & Boswellin®CG, which are proven to promote healthy hair growth, strengthen hair shaft and reduce hair loss in both male and female.

Key Benefits:

• Stimulates and reboots your hair follicles.

• Extremely effective in arresting hair fall

• A lightweight serum• Easy to apply

.• Non-sticky serum• Extremely user friendly.

• Helps to strengthen the root of hair.

• Controls hair fall.

Suggested Usage:

Spray 4 to 5 pumps of Anti Hair Fall Serum on scalp or palm.Gently massage the scalp for 5 to 10 minutes.Apply it daily after bath and avoid washing hair for 4 hours.

Ingredients:

Aqua, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Polysorbate 20, Propylene Glycol, Phenoxyethanol (and) Ethylhexylglycerin, Hydroxyethyl Cellulose, Polyquaternium-39, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Liquid Endosperm, Emblica Officinalis Fruit Extract (Saberry®), Fragrance, Nigella Sativa Seed Extract (Nigellin® Amber), Boswellia Serrata Resin Extract (Boswellin® CG), Fragrance, Disodium EDTA, Luteolin (Peanut Shell Extract), Methylseleno Carboxypropylglutamine (PeptiSeLect®), Tetrahydropiperine (Cosmoperine®). Nigellin® Amber, Saberry®, Boswellin® CG, PeptiSeLect® and Cosmoperine® are registered trademarks of Sabinsa Corporation, USA.
